<stack-static>
    <statement><p><p>Write the number <m>{8}</m> in index form with a prime base.</p>
<p><alert>Note:</alert> Your answer should be written as <m>a^b</m>, where <m>a</m> is <alert>prime</alert>.</p>

<p><fillin characters="6" name="ans1"/>  </p></p></statement>
    <solution><p><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>The number given is <m>{8}</m>.</p>

<p>We check if it can be written as repeated multiplication of the same base.</p>

<p><m>{8} = {2\times 2\times 2}</m></p>

<p>Therefore, the index form is <m>{2}^{3}</m>.</p></p></solution>
    <answer><p><m>2^3</m></p></answer>
</stack-static>